{"title":"普天同庆","authors":["郭沫若"],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":1,"day":28}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"普天同庆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"郭沫若"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在总路线的光辉照耀之下，1959年在1958年的大跃进的基础之上又继续大跃进。钢煤粮棉四大指标和其他重要生产品都以两年工夫超额完成了第二个五年计划。爰成“十六字令”四首，以志庆祝。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一马当先上战场，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奔腾烈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热浪卷红纲！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"煤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滚滚乌金出地维，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真力猛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烈焰吐明辉！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民公社威力扬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丰收庆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打倒大灾荒！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"棉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五年计划两年完，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人六亿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天下不知寒！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1960年1月24日"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}